    "In cases of studies with incomplete data, we have tried to contact the corresponding authors for clarification or additional information.",
    "Due to the diversity of investigated outcomes and study designs we sought to include, a meta-analysis was not practical.",
    "Instead, a data-driven convergent synthesis approach was selected for thematic syntheses of LLM applications and limitations in patient care 19.",
